        *************** Beginning of data ************************************* 
0002.00   dcl-s today date;                                                     
0002.01   dcl-s wdate packed(8:0) inz(20230702);                                
0003.00     today = %date(wdate);                                               
0004.00     dsply today;                                                        
0005.00   *INLR=*ON;                                                            
        ****************** End of data **************************************** 

%date function Example(2) - Convert numeric value to Date
